data.description: Incredible opportunity to make this open, split floor-plan 4-bedroom, 2 bath, 3 car garage home in Millers Glenn your very own! Meticulously kept finishes throughout including beautiful crown and chair rail molding, plantation shutters, granite throughout, gas fireplace with remote start, wi-fi enabled smart garage system, tons of space in the walk up attic to easily store items! Seamless transitions from hardwood floor to tile, kitchen pantry, oversized breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances, gas range, double oven! The master bath has jacuzzi tub, separate walk-in tile shower and large walk in-closet that goes through to the laundry room. Built in office area is next to the laundry. Security system, covered patio out back, with pet door access, playground stays! So much to offer! This is a must see!
